{"data":[{"id":560856216,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b55e51b0ff42e8cc231d21598a622f14","url_token":"dong-zhe-jian","name":"司空百味","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b77867b38e2ec03a4c5405884e3e990a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b77867b38e2ec03a4c5405884e3e990a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b55e51b0ff42e8cc231d21598a622f14","user_type":"people","headline":"想得却不可得，你奈人生何。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":70,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560856216","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545893873,"updated_time":1545963500,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"comment_count":38,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"nobody","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e终于可以说声辣鸡知乎现在的氛围还不如贴吧了，题主问的是解出来了能不能保送清华，一堆人在乎的却是他根本不可能解出来并阴阳怪气冷嘲热讽，还上升到国家教育学术层面（这中间有多少人对哥德巴赫猜想的了解还不如题主的），当然有些高赞的答主认真分析我觉得很棒。这就跟一个常年差生突然考到全级第一，所有人怀疑他是作弊的一样。仔细看看你们身边的人和你们自己的嘴脸，是不是最喜欢落井下石，通过打压来满足自己卑微的虚荣心。你从来不关心别人到底怎么样，你只想跟着群众满足口舌之快而已。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我退一万步来讲，就算一个高中生来知乎问了一个很蠢的问题，这就是你们这群“数学家”群起而攻之的理由？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不太明白，人家只是对自己的爱好抱有极大的热枕，并想用这种热枕上清华北大，只不过恰好他的爱好比较“宏伟”又广而告之了而已，各位键盘侠们又何必恶言相向冷嘲热讽呢？就算他的算法和证法出了错误，也不会影响任何人，也是受限于他的年龄而已。能对数学难题有兴趣和认真钻研本身就值得鼓励。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e任何一个努力认真的人都值得尊重。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"终于可以说声辣鸡知乎现在的氛围还不如贴吧了，题主问的是解出来了能不能保送清华，一堆人在乎的却是他根本不可能解出来并阴阳怪气冷嘲热讽，还上升到国家教育学术层面（这中间有多少人对哥德巴赫猜想的了解还不如题主的），当然有些高赞的答主认真分析我觉…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1826\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count